<div id="mturkoverlay" oncontextmenu="$('#canvas').focus(); return false;" onclick="$('#canvas').focus();">
  <div class="center">
    <input type="button" id="startButton" value="Start"/>
  </div>
  <div id = "wrap">
    <%= image_tag '', :id => 'targetImage' %>
  </div>
  <div id="editinstructions">
    <p id="prompt">Put mouse here for instructions</p>
    <div id="instructions">
      <p>Place objects in the room to create a scene that best resembles the picture on the left (mouse over to zoom).</p>
      <p>Find objects using the search bar on the right.
        Left click on search results and left click in the scene to place the object. Left-click drag to move objects.</p>
      <p>When an object is selected, drag the blue circle around it to rotate it, and drag the yellow arrows to resize it.
        Keyboard shortcuts: up and down arrow to resize, left and right arrow to rotate.</p>
      <p>To move the camera use right-click dragging and the mousewheel, or use the camera control button in the top left corner.</p>
      <p>Place at least 5 objects but feel free to add more so the room better resembles the picture.</p>
      <p>Click the "Save" button when you're done to receive a coupon.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
